WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

2
00:00:24.215 --> 00:00:26.979
I'm really sorry.

3
00:00:28.286 --> 00:00:29.514
Do you know...

4
00:00:29.754 --> 00:00:31.221
What was bothering him?

5
00:00:35.093 --> 00:00:36.617
No. Suddenly he...

6
00:00:36.828 --> 00:00:39.058
It's your gang's fault.

7
00:00:41.399 --> 00:00:43.128
Have you all gone insane?

8
00:00:44.435 --> 00:00:46.027
What do you mean?

9
00:00:47.205 --> 00:00:49.173
You've all committed suicide.

10
00:00:50.508 --> 00:00:51.634
Who?

11
00:00:53.044 --> 00:00:54.477
Don't you know?

12
00:00:55.146 --> 00:00:56.613
The other two...

13
00:00:57.014 --> 00:00:59.039
also killed themselves.

14
00:00:59.751 --> 00:01:00.979
Which two?

15
00:01:04.255 --> 00:01:08.055
The two who sat next to you.

16
00:01:52.370 --> 00:01:53.803
Who's this woman?

17
00:01:58.176 --> 00:01:59.575
Where did you get that?

18
00:02:00.845 --> 00:02:02.904
She's the shadow in the photos. right?

19
00:02:04.549 --> 00:02:05.709
Who is she?

20
00:02:08.619 --> 00:02:10.587
How is she related to you?

21
00:02:28.940 --> 00:02:30.908
I knew her in college.

22
00:02:34.011 --> 00:02:35.501
Her name is Natre.

23
00:02:39.083 --> 00:02:41.074
She was a quiet person...

24
00:02:42.820 --> 00:02:44.185
without any friends.

25
00:02:48.326 --> 00:02:50.191
We all thought she was weird.

26
00:02:55.366 --> 00:02:56.958
I felt sorry for her.

27
00:03:04.208 --> 00:03:06.403
We dated but I kept it secret.

28
00:03:09.947 --> 00:03:11.312
She loved me a lot.

29
00:06:02.486 --> 00:06:04.181
She threatened to slit her wrists.

30
00:06:05.990 --> 00:06:07.617
I didn't know what to do.

31
00:06:08.192 --> 00:06:09.887
My friends thought it was funny.

32
00:06:10.394 --> 00:06:11.918
How were they involved?

33
00:06:12.463 --> 00:06:13.760
Why are they dead?

34
00:06:14.365 --> 00:06:15.491
They...

35
00:06:15.699 --> 00:06:16.757
What did they do?

36
00:06:19.203 --> 00:06:20.431
I don't know.

37
00:06:21.806 --> 00:06:24.172
Tonn said he'd take care of it.

38
00:06:28.112 --> 00:06:29.807
After that. Natre disappeared.

39
00:06:31.649 --> 00:06:33.674
I never saw her again.

40
00:06:34.685 --> 00:06:36.778
Didn't you try to stop them?

41
00:06:38.889 --> 00:06:41.551
How could you let it happen?

42
00:06:48.099 --> 00:06:49.589
What could I do?

43
00:06:52.002 --> 00:06:53.629
Now everyone is dead.

44
00:06:57.174 --> 00:06:58.402
I'm...

45
00:06:59.376 --> 00:07:00.900
I'm going to die next.

46
00:07:39.650 --> 00:07:40.947
It's funny how...

47
00:07:43.287 --> 00:07:45.187
we always say...

48
00:07:46.123 --> 00:07:47.886
if we could turn back time...

49
00:07:49.660 --> 00:07:50.592
we...

50
00:07:50.828 --> 00:07:52.796
we would reverse all our wrongs.

51
00:07:56.200 --> 00:07:57.827
Do you think she's okay?

52
00:07:59.270 --> 00:08:00.635
Will she be there?

53
00:08:01.071 --> 00:08:02.163
Go to sleep.

54
00:08:04.775 --> 00:08:06.265
I'll keep you company tonight.

55
00:10:10.901 --> 00:10:12.061
Excuse me.

56
00:10:13.370 --> 00:10:14.803
Do you have any toilet paper?

57
00:10:49.807 --> 00:10:51.206
Can I poo first?

58
00:10:51.408 --> 00:10:52.807
I'm sorry.

59
00:12:01.945 --> 00:12:03.173
What's bothering you?

60
00:12:17.027 --> 00:12:18.585
Tun. What's wrong?

61
00:12:30.707 --> 00:12:32.072
What is it?

62
00:13:23.727 --> 00:13:24.989
Is it around here?

63
00:13:35.906 --> 00:13:37.203
Excuse me.

64
00:13:37.808 --> 00:13:39.070
Do you know where this is?

65
00:13:43.480 --> 00:13:45.380
Mom. where is this house?

66
00:14:19.349 --> 00:14:20.611
Ma'am.

67
00:14:33.130 --> 00:14:34.222
Excuse me...

68
00:14:34.464 --> 00:14:35.863
Is this Natre's house?

69
00:14:37.834 --> 00:14:38.994
What do you want?

70
00:14:40.304 --> 00:14:41.328
Well...

71
00:14:41.705 --> 00:14:43.866
We're her friends.

72
00:14:44.841 --> 00:14:46.832
Natre's friends? Come inside.

73
00:14:57.921 --> 00:15:00.389
Have some water. You must be tired.

74
00:15:00.724 --> 00:15:02.316
Did you drive from Bangkok?

75
00:15:03.527 --> 00:15:04.551
Yes.

76
00:15:07.664 --> 00:15:11.691
We'd like to ask about Natre.

77
00:15:12.736 --> 00:15:14.397
She's not feeling well.

78
00:15:14.805 --> 00:15:16.102
She's taking a nap.

79
00:15:17.608 --> 00:15:19.007
Should I wake her?

80
00:15:23.380 --> 00:15:24.972
Stay for dinner.

81
00:15:25.849 --> 00:15:27.077
I was about to cook.

82
00:15:27.284 --> 00:15:29.650
I'm making her favourite dish.

83
00:15:31.355 --> 00:15:32.913
Natre will be so happy.

84
00:15:33.423 --> 00:15:35.254
Her friends don't visit often.

85
00:15:35.859 --> 00:15:37.258
Wait right here.

86
00:15:56.213 --> 00:15:57.475
Where are you going?

87
00:17:12.122 --> 00:17:13.419
How dare you?

88
00:17:19.463 --> 00:17:21.431
Did she commit suicide?

89
00:17:26.369 --> 00:17:28.496
We should cremate her.

90
00:17:30.440 --> 00:17:31.407
No.

91
00:17:31.608 --> 00:17:32.973
I won't cremate her.

92
00:17:35.412 --> 00:17:36.401
Ma'am...

93
00:17:38.048 --> 00:17:40.915
I don't know if you believe such things...

94
00:17:41.384 --> 00:17:44.751
but I'd like you to look at these photos.

95
00:17:45.555 --> 00:17:48.888
They were taken around campus.

96
00:17:51.194 --> 00:17:53.526
Some of the places...

97
00:17:54.297 --> 00:17:57.198
were rooms Natre had been in.

98
00:17:58.034 --> 00:18:01.970
And these shadows appeared

99
00:18:05.542 --> 00:18:06.770
I think that...

100
00:18:08.011 --> 00:18:11.105
Natre's spirit is restless.

101
00:18:12.582 --> 00:18:13.810
Natre...

102
00:18:17.454 --> 00:18:18.921
My dear Natre.

103
00:18:21.124 --> 00:18:23.024
Why don't you visit me?

104
00:18:31.501 --> 00:18:33.901
Can you tell me what happened?

105
00:18:34.805 --> 00:18:36.466
Why she left Bangkok?

106
00:18:44.981 --> 00:18:46.243
Ma'am...

107
00:18:48.485 --> 00:18:49.645
Ma'am.

108
00:18:51.021 --> 00:18:52.648
These shadows...

109
00:18:53.223 --> 00:18:56.556
might mean her spirit is not at peace.

110
00:19:00.897 --> 00:19:03.092
We should hold her funeral.

111
00:19:04.634 --> 00:19:05.965
Please.

112
00:19:20.150 --> 00:19:21.378
When she came home...

113
00:19:21.585 --> 00:19:23.018
she seemed different.

114
00:19:23.386 --> 00:19:25.149
She wouldn't talk to anyone.

115
00:19:25.722 --> 00:19:27.713
No one knows what happened in Bangkok.

116
00:19:29.693 --> 00:19:31.854
Then she overdosed on pills.

117
00:19:32.562 --> 00:19:34.962
Luckily. her mother found her...

118
00:19:35.332 --> 00:19:37.197
and got her to the hospital on time.

119
00:19:37.701 --> 00:19:39.965
When she recovered...

120
00:19:41.304 --> 00:19:44.171
she climbed on the hospital roof...

121
00:19:44.808 --> 00:19:46.332
and jumped off the edge.

122
00:19:48.511 --> 00:19:51.275
Why wouldn't her mom cremate her?

123
00:19:53.383 --> 00:19:56.614
She's been distraught
ever since Natre's death.

124
00:19:57.354 --> 00:20:01.017
No matter what she refused to cremate her.

125
00:20:02.359 --> 00:20:04.554
All the villagers were scared.

126
00:20:04.928 --> 00:20:07.726
No one wanted to socialize with her.

127
00:22:10.453 --> 00:22:11.681
Can't sleep?

128
00:22:17.494 --> 00:22:19.553
Tell me the truth...

129
00:22:20.530 --> 00:22:22.191
Did you love Natre?

130
00:22:26.002 --> 00:22:27.731
I tried to...

131
00:22:34.010 --> 00:22:36.501
I believed that one day I would.

132
00:22:42.252 --> 00:22:44.152
But I was fooling myself.

133
00:22:52.162 --> 00:22:53.595
When I broke it off...

134
00:22:54.831 --> 00:22:57.265
I was a total asshole.

135
00:23:03.273 --> 00:23:05.207
But she still loved me the same.

136
00:23:11.781 --> 00:23:13.612
I want this to be over.

137
00:23:15.685 --> 00:23:18.119
If she wants me to die I will.

138
00:23:19.189 --> 00:23:20.850
Don't say that.

139
00:23:21.858 --> 00:23:23.450
It's almost over.

140
00:23:24.828 --> 00:23:25.954
No it's not.

141
00:23:31.134 --> 00:23:33.398
I know she'll come for me.

142
00:23:34.304 --> 00:23:35.362
Tun.

143
00:23:36.272 --> 00:23:37.933
We've come this far.

144
00:23:40.276 --> 00:23:42.244
And you're sorry for what you did.

145
00:23:43.213 --> 00:23:44.771
I'm sure she knows.

146
00:23:47.150 --> 00:23:48.777
Don't talk about death anymore.

147
00:23:55.892 --> 00:23:57.291
I'm sorry.

148
00:24:02.932 --> 00:24:04.695
Do you still love me?

149
00:24:10.640 --> 00:24:13.473
No matter what you won't leave me. right?

150
00:25:52.675 --> 00:25:54.700
Jane.

151
00:27:27.804 --> 00:27:29.101
Tun...

152
00:27:29.472 --> 00:27:30.461
Jane...

153
00:27:31.007 --> 00:27:32.497
Where did you go?

154
00:27:33.810 --> 00:27:35.300
Why did you leave me alone?

155
00:27:36.212 --> 00:27:37.304
We've got to leave.

156
00:27:40.917 --> 00:27:42.316
Asshole!

157
00:27:43.553 --> 00:27:45.020
Why did you leave me?

158
00:27:45.221 --> 00:27:46.916
Didn't you love me?

159
00:27:47.357 --> 00:27:48.654
How could you leave me?

160
00:27:51.728 --> 00:27:53.593
How could you leave me?

161
00:29:32.929 --> 00:29:34.123
Tun...

162
00:29:34.497 --> 00:29:36.055
Are you feeling better?

163
00:29:38.601 --> 00:29:40.592
What happened last night?

164
00:29:42.071 --> 00:29:43.129
Tun...

165
00:29:44.807 --> 00:29:45.774
Jane...

166
00:29:45.975 --> 00:29:47.101
Jane...

167
00:29:54.250 --> 00:29:55.182
The abbot said...

168
00:29:55.384 --> 00:29:57.352
Natre will be cremated today.

169
00:30:00.990 --> 00:30:02.548
It's over.

170
00:31:58.441 --> 00:31:59.999
- Hello.
- Hello. Jane.

171
00:32:00.610 --> 00:32:01.634
Picking up photos?

172
00:32:02.445 --> 00:32:03.343
Where's Tun?

173
00:32:03.546 --> 00:32:04.774
He's busy.

174
00:32:05.247 --> 00:32:06.339
Good.

175
00:32:06.549 --> 00:32:07.379
When he's busy...

176
00:32:07.583 --> 00:32:09.050
I get to see you.

177
00:32:17.159 --> 00:32:18.490
You went on vacation?

178
00:32:19.328 --> 00:32:20.386
To the beach.

179
00:32:20.930 --> 00:32:22.056
When did you go?

180
00:32:22.765 --> 00:32:24.289
Last week.

181
00:32:26.636 --> 00:32:28.627
This photo is...

182
00:32:32.141 --> 00:32:33.301
What's wrong?

183
00:32:39.482 --> 00:32:40.710
You look fatter.

184
00:32:43.085 --> 00:32:44.484
I didn't recognize you.

185
00:32:46.989 --> 00:32:47.956
Hi.

186
00:32:48.958 --> 00:32:50.152
Jumbo prints.

187
00:32:51.861 --> 00:32:53.089
Write you name. please.

188
00:35:32.555 --> 00:35:33.817
Get her guys!

189
00:36:09.491 --> 00:36:10.583
Jane...

190
00:36:10.993 --> 00:36:12.722
Why are you crying?

191
00:36:15.631 --> 00:36:16.723
Asshole...

192
00:36:19.335 --> 00:36:21.303
How could you be so cruel?

193
00:36:26.942 --> 00:36:28.375
Where did you find these?

194
00:36:30.980 --> 00:36:32.572
If I didn't find them...

195
00:36:32.781 --> 00:36:35.011
I'd be a fool forever. right?

196
00:36:40.623 --> 00:36:42.113
Let me explain.

197
00:36:45.361 --> 00:36:47.056
What's there to say?

198
00:36:51.400 --> 00:36:52.992
I always believed you.

199
00:37:00.109 --> 00:37:02.043
I thought I knew you.

200
00:37:16.025 --> 00:37:17.083
Tun.

201
00:37:18.327 --> 00:37:19.453
Take her picture...

202
00:37:19.728 --> 00:37:20.922
so she doesn't blab.

203
00:37:21.130 --> 00:37:23.121
Tun. help me.

204
00:37:24.800 --> 00:37:25.960
I know it was wrong.

205
00:37:27.603 --> 00:37:29.400
Take her picture now!

206
00:37:30.572 --> 00:37:31.698
What's wrong!

207
00:37:33.242 --> 00:37:34.709
I'm your buddy!

208
00:37:35.210 --> 00:37:36.234
Hurry!

209
00:37:44.920 --> 00:37:46.751
Tun. help me.

210
00:38:00.202 --> 00:38:01.499
I never forgave myself.

211
00:38:01.704 --> 00:38:03.672
But I was young and stupid.

212
00:38:05.240 --> 00:38:06.605
I've heard enough.

213
00:38:08.711 --> 00:38:10.201
I'm going home.

214
00:39:05.100 --> 00:39:06.431
Come on out!

215
00:39:11.240 --> 00:39:12.605
Where are you?

216
00:39:19.148 --> 00:39:20.775
I thought you loved me!

217
00:39:23.118 --> 00:39:24.813
Loved me so much!

218
00:39:32.294 --> 00:39:34.489
Till death do us part!

219
00:39:39.601 --> 00:39:41.228
She's gone now.

220
00:41:20.502 --> 00:41:21.730
Sometimes...

221
00:41:21.970 --> 00:41:24.302
spirits long for their loved ones.

222
00:41:25.305 --> 00:42:25.161
